2. Bg5 e6 ( { There are many setups Black can choose against the Trompowsky, but there are two moves for Black that are played the most often: } 2...e6 { and } ) ( 2...Ne4 { . In this chapter we will focus on } ) ( 2...e6 { . } ) 
