18. Rxc6 { And White is winning with the extra piece. } *

[Event "The Trompowsky: Simplified"]
[White "6) Pseudo-Trompowsky: 1...d5 2.Bg5 h6"]
[Black "3...c5 and 4...cxd4 #9"]
[Date "2023.01.02"]
