10. Nc3 { By playing Nc3 and then Nb5 White keeps the a6-knight stuck on its passive square on the edge of the board, and also the rook on a8 cannot move so easily because a7 would drop. } e6 
11. Nb5 Be7 
12. Bg3 Nf6 
