14. Nb3 {[%cal Gf3d4,Rd7a4,Gh4e7][%csl Ra2]} { The Black queen is getting locked in and we will use this fact to gain time to activate the rest of our pieces. Play through the remaining moves to see how play could develop. } Ba4 ( { On } 14...Bd6 { White can take on e7 followed by Qxd5 because at the end the bishop on d6 is attacked by the white queen. } ) 
