2. d5 Nf6 { Black is hoping White will play c2-c4 with transposition to a main line Benko or Benoni, but White has different plans. There are two good options and I give them both so you can decide which one you prefer. } ( { If Black instead plays } 2...d6 { we transpose to the line with } 3.Nc3 Nf6 { . } ) 
